rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0001
rows.name: The city of Gula is always peaceful.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm part of the self-defense
corps, and I've got more
than enough free time.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The Superbian Empire's garrison is here
too, so people who try to cause trouble
in this city are a rare sight.

rows.label: tlk41300022_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It seems there was a little
incident, but well, it's
probably nothing serious...
